                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 1ra-6v), fragment
 I-I)
                     Introduction (fols. 1ra-vb, 3ra l.13)
 - Story of the family of Adam (fols.
                     1ra-vb, 3ra l.13), incomplete
 I-2) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus”: 2
                     miracles (fol. 3ra l.13-6vb), incomplete.</summary>
